    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or snow. The exterior features the original factory paint, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like gloss with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are pristine, devoid of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery still carries that new-car scent, with no creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is spotless. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
